title: The Negative S'more
description:
Camp Chef S'more of the week | The Negative S'more

A non-traditional s'more recipe, The Negative S'more is loaded with chocolate flavor, provides a fun and interesting twist, and like all the others, is easy to make.

Ingredients:

• Chocolate Graham
• Marshmallow
• Cookies and Creme Chocolate
